---
title: Roasted Cherry Tomato Spaghetti with Arugula and Citrus Chicken
description: Roasting cherry tomatoes is the simplest way to turn them spectacular. We're pairing these sweet gems with arugula for a simple pasta dish, topped with a lemony chicken!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-cherry-tomato-spaghetti-2ccf37a3.jpg
